<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Abonnement Pro active</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f8fafc;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color:#f8fafc;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:48px 16px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" style="max-width:540px;">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:28px;">
              {% include 'emails/_brand_header.html.twig' %}
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);overflow:hidden;">
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:#059669;height:3px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:40px 40px 36px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#059669;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Abonnement Pro</p>
                    <h1 style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1e293b;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.3px;">
                      Votre paiement a ete confirme
                    </h1>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;">
                      Felicitations. Votre abonnement <strong style="color:#1e293b;">MYKEYNEST Pro</strong> est maintenant actif.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 28px;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.7;">
                      Il ne vous reste plus qu a definir votre mot de passe pour acceder a votre espace et commencer a utiliser MYKEYNEST.
                    </p>
                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin-bottom:28px;">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="border-radius:8px;background:#059669;">
                          <a href="{{ setup_url }}" style="display:inline-block;padding:13px 28px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;">
                            Creer mon mot de passe
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;">
                          <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;">
                            Ce lien expire le <strong style="color:#1e293b;">{{ expiresAt|date('d/m/Y a H:i') }}</strong>.
                            Si besoin, vous pourrez toujours demander un nouveau lien depuis la page de connexion.
                          </p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
